    "See Appendix I for all the prompts used in our experiments.",
    "We follow standard evaluation practices and report the F1 score for all the datasets.",
    "Following Radford et al. (2019), we evaluate yes-no question answering and NLI using ranked classification, i.e., we generate the loglikelihood of all the choices and choose the sequence with the highest loglikelihood as the prediction.",
    "Following Rajpurkar et al.",
    "(2016), we evaluate models on extractive question answering by computing the SQuAD F1 score on the generated output."
